{
  "stem": "13851.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Poznan ?] on the border of Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they shipped them out from there they lived-- where they lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they came all, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Konin, ?] [INAUDIBLE] towns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I remember there was people living with my uncle and a lot of people in the same town, same ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the ghetto was the name of my hometown.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- the only thing what they did is they take that who needed for work, they went in the ghetto, and they-- they took us out to go to work for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and the same time was, they made a Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Judenrat means some oldest people to organize for them what they wanted to do something for the people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like they want people [INAUDIBLE] Judenrat, 'We need-- need 1,000 boys to work,' or something, so a few hundred boys [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they took us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had the order from them to do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or they-- they want money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They should get money out of the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And otherwise, they're going to kill us out, or something like that, they're warning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's what the Judenrat was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did what they want, tell them what to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then you had to do all the-- do things for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you know people who were in the Judenrat in your ghetto?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I mean, we know the people, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure, but you couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that they-- they have to do what they wanted-- told them to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and they thought they were going to do it like going to work, giving what-- the money what they want, that's [INAUDIBLE] quiet them down.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then, you know, they did-- they what they told them to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
